{"tid":1045294,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)盜墓迷城1-3","createTime":"2019-03-03T13:28:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T19:21:18.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ade44731ad1c0c2d599bacdce143d491f77374c2","tid":1045294,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T13:28:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=k%2BTG7AB%2FuAEPzMnKacyWvyZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=17cac5be\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=k%2BTG7AB%2FuAEPzMnKacyWvyZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=81f58827\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=k%2BTG7AB%2FuAEPzMnKacyWvyZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=ecce93ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n1.公元前1290年，埃及底比斯大祭司印和闐與法老塞提一世的夫人安克&middot;姍&middot;娜曼有了私情，法老發現他們幽會後被兩人所殺。塞提的衛兵發現後，印和闐成功逃脫，而安克&middot;姍&middot;娜曼自殺了。印和闐和手下的祭司在安克&middot;姍&middot;娜曼下葬後盜出她的屍體並前往亡靈之城哈姆納塔（Hamunaptra），開始儀式試圖將她復活。但塞提的衛兵意外出現，儀式因此未能成功，安克&middot;姍&middot;娜曼的靈魂又回到了地下世界。印和闐手下的祭司被活生生地製成木乃伊，印和闐則被判要永生永世承受詛咒..<br />\n<br />\n2.劇情設定在第一集的九年後（西元1933年），探險家瑞克‧歐康納和愛人艾芙琳結婚了，兩人幸福的定居在倫敦，還有個八歲的小兒子艾力克斯。就在歐康納一家到埃及度假時，偶然地在一處神廟遺跡內發現一條古代的黃金手環（但實際上是「死神之環」，The Bracelet of Anubis）。但很快地，他們就被一群不肖人士給盯上，目的則是為了那條金手環。在一陣混亂的情況下，遺跡坍塌了，歐康納一家倉皇回到倫敦住處（手環也跟著帶了回來），而頑皮的小艾力克斯在把玩手環的時候不慎戴了上去，接著看到了手環投射出的影像後驚訝不已，但回過神時才發現手環已經拿不下來..<br />\n<br />\n3.電影開始時由旁白介紹在二千多年前，當時中國處於戰國時代末年，分裂成好幾個國家，天下大亂，唯有一位霸主（李連杰飾），劇中稱龍皇帝，他很有野心，而且所向披靡，別的國家派刺客（吳京飾）去殺他，但刺客反給他殺死，他又從方士那兒學懂修煉五行之術&mdash;&mdash;金、木、水、火、土。不久他便統一天下，成為皇帝，他奴役俘虜，要他們修築長城，並將所有死的、傷的都埋在長城下，並施法令他們變成守城靈魂。皇帝擊敗了當時所有敵人，剩下來要面對的是所有人都要面對的問題&mdash;&mdash;死亡..<br />\n<br />\n9 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=k%2BTG7AB%2FuAEPzMnKacyWvyZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=f21b88b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=k%2BTG7AB%2FuAEPzMnKacyWvyZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=4422f20f\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6051e38aa5ef3b28ffcaaac02ca90512521e028f","tid":1045294,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T13:28:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/6/68/The_mummy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F6%2F68%2FThe_mummy.jpg&h=6413c730&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ead61c68418a15433d3edd7a9dbe77da5f513cbf","tid":1045294,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T14:04:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2833092434fe1602121d9f6ba5752d695d7223cf","tid":1045294,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T15:32:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db6f3d83e4ca24953efe8d9912dbe66a77d1dbca","tid":1045294,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T16:42:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"576706b4467621f0ce7d89b6936557065c0a040a","tid":1045294,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T18:14:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4752a91c272b23e00942e7dcaf0fbc7b813021f","tid":1045294,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T19:21:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}